    "description": "Level 8 Conjuration (Druid, Sorcerer, Wizard) Casting Time: Action Range: 150 feet Components: V, S Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute A swirling cloud of embers and smoke fills a 20-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point within range. The cloud\u2019s area is Heavily Obscured. It lasts for the duration or until a strong wind (like that created by Gust of Wind ) disperses it. When the cloud appears, each creature in it makes a Dexterity saving throw, taking 10d8 Fire damage on a failed save or half as much damage on a successful one. A creature must also make this save when the Sphere moves into its space and when it enters the Sphere or ends its turn there. A creature makes this save only once per turn. The cloud moves 10 feet away from you in a direction you choose at the start of each of your turns.",
